This Implementation Plan provides a complete roadmap from infrastructure setup
to pilot completion. Key highlights:

âœ… Technology Stack: React + TypeScript + Supabase (proven for scale, fast dev)
âœ… Database Schema: 13 tables with RLS, indexes, materialized views (ready to implement)
âœ… Sprint Breakdown: 8 weeks to MVP, 4 weeks pilot, 2 weeks iteration
âœ… Technical Challenges: Solutions for virtualization, similarity detection, real-time sync
âœ… Risk Mitigation: 10 identified risks with owners and mitigation plans
âœ… Pilot Plan: Integrated 30-45 day pilot with clear go/no-go criteria

Next Steps:
